data.description: Great find in the coveted Estates at Tanoan! This home has been lovingly cared for by it's current owner and features a traditional floor plan with 2 living areas, 2 dining areas, a sweeping staircase, a main floor primary suite, and an office all on the main floor. Upstairs, there is a second primary suite with an en-suite bathroom, and two additional bedrooms with a jack and Jill bath. The oversized 3 car garage offers plenty of storage. Beautiful windows let in lots of natural light, and cathedral ceilings add to the open feel.  The backyard offers great patio space for entertaining and is nice and private. This home is conveniently located in the NE Heights with quick and easy access to shopping, dining, great schools, and entertainment.
